snippet.textDisplay: This season had some very excellent acrobatic acts. But I have to say that balancing board act with the mother and the two men is the most thrilling, if not the most dangerous act I have ever seen, and I have seen everything. It's a breath of fresh air not to have a singing act win time and time again. I personally think the singing acts belong on the Voice or the American Idol. But of course it sucks that the AI limits the ages of the contestants.
